Class RelHomogeneousShuttle

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.rel.RelShuttleImpl

    public class RelHomogeneousShuttle
extends RelShuttleImpl
    Visits all the relations in a homogeneous way: always redirects calls to accept(RelNode).
